  <parts>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>What the scrolls called a dazzling river port is now no more than crumbling stones perched at the edge of a dry riverbed. The only other detail of note is an agglomeration of unusually dense fumes hanging over the dusty gulch.

After an unsuccessful attempt to peer through this unhealthy looking cloud, you turn back and are startled to find a young man standing only a few feet behind you. He is empty-handed and dressed in old robes, many times patched and too threadbare to conceal any weapons.

"What do you seek here?" he asks. Though you have spoken with people from many lands, his accent is strange to you.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>aod.npc_rvr_man_met = true;</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I’m looking for an old temple.”</text>
          <def_link>1</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>0</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“The Great Ziggurat,” nods the man. “It lies beyond the hollow.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“The hollow?”</text>
          <def_link>2</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>1</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“It was a lake once, but the Gods cursed it,” explains the man. “They sent an evil wind that brought death to everyone who hadn’t gone into hiding and caused the waters to boil and turn to poison.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“How do I get across?”</text>
          <def_link>3</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“The evil wind?”</text>
          <def_link>13</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>2</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“There came a wind, heralded by thunder, and it fell upon the town like a hammer,” recites the man, struggling to remember the words, “scorching the earth and withering every flower. A dark cloud covered the land like a cloak, hiding it from the sun, and the earth trembled to its core.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“So how do I get across?”</text>
          <def_link>3</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>13</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Were you summoned?” asks the man with childlike curiously.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Yes.”</text>
          <def_link>4</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“No.”</text>
          <def_link>5</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>3</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Then the Gods will send for you,” says the man with conviction.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“And if they don't?”</text>
          <def_link>5</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Then you must take the trial and prove that you’re worthy.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“A trial?”</text>
          <def_link>6</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>5</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“The hollow is dry, so you can cross it on foot. The air isn’t as bad as before, but it will weaken you all the same when you need your strength the most.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why?”</text>
          <def_link>7</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>6</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“The evil wind killed everything that walks but spared things that crawl because the Gods had a special task for them. The Gods ordered them to grow big and guard the hollow, until the curse is lifted and the waters return to wash them away.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Let me guess, giant scorpions? They never go out of style, do they?”</text>
          <def_link>8</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>7</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“They are fearsome and terrifying beasts,” agrees the man.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“There is no other way across?”</text>
          <def_link>9</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>11</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Not anymore,” says the young man.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“But there used to be?”</text>
          <def_link>10</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“There are stories of a bridge made of light, but I must confess that I have a hard time imagining such a thing. What man is worthy enough to walk on light?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Who can tell me more about that bridge of light?”</text>
          <def_link>12</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>10</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>END</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
        <string>dlgFinish();</string>
        <string>dlgFadeShortToThisPart();</string>
        <string>dlgTeleportToMarker(TM_Novice, 8505);</string>
      </onLoadScripts>
      <answers />
      <UID>11</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“For a small donation the Elder will be happy to answer your questions,” says the man promptly - probably the main reason he was sent to greet you. He points at the stone steps disappearing into darkness.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>11</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>12</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Blessed be,” says the man, watching you with interest.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Leave.</text>
          <def_link>11</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>14</UID>
